<div class="govuk-body">
  <div class="govuk-grid-row">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">

      <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">Find facilities management services suppliers</h1>

      <p>Use this service to:</p>

      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>find facilities management services suppliers for one place or multiple locations</li>
      </ul>

      <%= link_to 'Start now', journey_start_path(journey: FacilitiesManagement::Journey.journey_name), role: 'button', class: 'govuk-button govuk-button--start govuk-!-margin-top-2 govuk-!-margin-bottom-8' %>

      <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Before you start</h2>

      <p>To use the service, you will need to know:</p>

      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>the region where the services need to be delivered, including if this is at more than one location</li>
        <li>the value of your current contract - if you don’t have a current contract, or are changing what’s included, you’ll need to base your selection on the estimated total contract value</li>
      </ul>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
